revisions.description: Updated RBN/rbn/Rbn as ERICSSON-ROUTER/eriRouter/EriRouter to migrate RBN MIB to ERICSSON MIB.
Update DESCRIPTION clause of MODULE-IDENTITY and PRODUCT-RELEASE clause of AGENT-CAPABILITIES.
Modified PRODUCT-RELEASE clause for consistent naming.
(1) Add eriRouterIetfMauCapSE for SmartEdge 6.1.3. (2) Update CONTACT-INFO (3) Update SmartEdge MAU-MIB based on RFC4836 (4) Update PRODUCT-RELEASE with the prefix AOS for SMS releases

eriRouterIetfMauCap.contactinfo: Ericsson AB. Postal: 100 Headquarters Dr San Jose, CA 95134 USA Phone: +1 408 750 5000 Fax: +1 408 750 5599
eriRouterIetfMauCap.description: The Agent Capabilities of the implementation of the IETF MAU-MIB (RFC2668). The Agent Capabilities of SmartEdge 6.1.3 IETF MAU-MIB is based on RFC4836 If this MIB implementation is platform-dependent, the PRODUCT-RELEASE clause contains Ericsson SEOS version and at least one of the following Ericsson product families: [SE] SmartEdge Multi-service Edge Router (MSER) family [SM] SM family of Metro Ethernet Service Transport platforms [SSR] Smart Service Router (SSR) family
